        "description": "Beam diameter for precise industrial cleaning; 200 μm recommended for birch surface preparation (fine detail for contamination removal). Smaller (100-200 μm) for detailed work, larger (300-500 μm) for broad areas. Source: Equipment specs from Coherent and Trumpf laser systems."
